{"tid":1057860,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"驚訝大仔Lucas大得快 張栢芝：已經高過我","createTime":"2019-03-12T07:10:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T05:35:15.000Z","uid":135867,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b17d19eda2aca3f19a26fe04947433ffcc4326","tid":1057860,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"細仔個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張栢芝最近活躍於社交網站，她日前就上載一張大仔Lucas的近照，相中可見Lucas正在低頭玩手機，第一眼看過去跟爸爸謝霆鋒非常相似，果然盡得爸爸真傳！<br />\n她留言：「剛剛一落樓下見到有個男仔，我心裏在想邊個靚仔咁早去我屋企，原來係自己個仔，真係不敢相信他們的長大速度轉變快過香港的天氣報告，每一天高幾吋，現在已經高過我了怎麼辦？」<br />\n其實Lucas今年只得11歲，不過已經比媽媽高，相信長大後肯定是一名小鮮肉！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/esbunru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fesbunru.jpg&h=e4290994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"609031bc08e172d7c7ecf1bebf05c14d134b8fb5","tid":1057860,"uid":211461,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:13:15.000Z","msg":"佢會唔會拎老母啲閃卡黎J? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfd1551ca0039dcad6a20e3ce4e608ce8ae1283","tid":1057860,"uid":94454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"柏g好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e49681cb857228f6fe23a496a2a3b8db8ddd9b","tid":1057860,"uid":5077,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bfd1551ca0039dcad6a20e3ce4e608ce8ae1283","tid":1057860,"uid":94454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:19:04.000Z","msg":"柏g好大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:22:23.000Z","msg":"應該仲餵緊人奶"},{"pid":"20fb4964ed4fe43d94284aa92239010cef9b0901","tid":1057860,"uid":211461,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99e